  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Taste Lake Iseo's famous Franciacorta sparkling wine and walk through Bardolino's vineyards this summer, on this wine-lovers multi-centre holiday.</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e79223a789ae41bfa4325c78bb1c9ef9}" title="Lake Iseo">Lake Iseo</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> means you get to experience the tranquility and history of two stunning Italian lakes. Spend a few days walking around Lake Iseo, discovering art projects and sipping sparkling wine, before heading to Lake Garda, where you can stroll around vineyards and taste local wines in <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a>.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,765pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options:</h3>
<ul>
<li>7, 10, 11 or 14 nights accommodation in your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Travel on Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Return airport transfers to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Taxi transfers between your chosen destinations</li>
<li>Up to two included guided walks per person per week if staying in Lake Iseo &amp; Bardolino</li>
</ul>
