<p style="text-align: center;"><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 3 nights in a Standard Room at Hotel Ambra, Lake Iseo and 4 nights in a Standard Room at Park Hotel Gritti, Bardolino, with shared transfers between resorts, departing on the 21st May 25 from London Gatwick Airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 09/12/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
